metadata.name: AI 2041 Collector Card 01: Brendan Dawes
metadata.description:
The seven AI 2041 Collector Cards reflect the seven artists who participated in the curated TRLab x AI 2041 collection. The artworks represent two promising emerging technologies: AI and blockchain. 

The Collector Cards were distributed to the participants of this first of its kind collaboration. This NFT Collector Card celebrates artist 01 â€” Brendan Dawes, and the 61 collectors who own his artwork.
